data.title: Arthur Wilkinson
data.meta_description: Arthur Wilkinson. Composer: Wer ist Kendall Brown?. Arthur Wilkinson was born on 3 September 1919 in Ealing, London, England, UK. He was a composer, known for Wer ist Kendall Brown? (1953), A Song for Tomorrow (1948) and Melodies for You (1967). He was married to Dorothy Ann Henning. He died in 1968 in Hammersmith, London, England, UK.
